HOME.ENCRYPTED_PROTECTED_BY: Ukuqinisekiswa, kuqinisekisiwe kwaye kuvikelwe yiStellar Security
HOME.WITHOUT_TRACE_DESCRIPTION: Siqinisekisa ukuvikelwa okuphezulu kweenkcukacha zakho ezibucayi. Yonke idatha ihlaziywa kwindawo yomthengi. Asazi i-IP yakho, into oyabelana ngayo, okanye kubani oyabelana naye ngale miqolo yeemfihlo - kwaye okubalulekileyo, umxholo.
HOME.PRIVACY_PROTECTED_DESCRIPTION: Ungumntu kuphela owaziyo ikhonkco kwiinkcukacha ezifihliweyo ozilungiselele kunye nalowo umabelana naye. Xa uqala umyalezo, ungongeza iiphasiwedi phambi kokuba kuvulwe. Kungenzeka ukuba ubeke ixesha lokubhubhisa. Nokuba kunjalo, umyalezo ufihlwe emva kweentsuku ezili-14.
HOME.END_TO_END_ENCRYPTED_DESCRIPTION: Onke amakhonkco kunye nomxholo amaxhonywe kwindawo yomthengi, kuthetha ukuba asazi nokuthi ikhonkco nomxholo. Ngamnye ikhonkco inenombolo eyingqayizivele ye-36 ebhalwe ngendlela enye yokupakishwa ukuze ufikelele kuMnyalezo weMfihlo kunye nomxholo wayo ogciniwe nge-AES-256.
